race.comment: POP'S MAESTRO (7) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 13 lengths at this track in a handy 25.24. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Expected to measure up again. UNRULY BOY (2) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. In the money last time at this track (25.57) in a Grade 5, finishing a half a length second. Can feature with the right run. STREET MACHINE (1) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (25.81) at this track. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Leading chance. ROCKABYE BABY (8) won as expected last time and is sure to feature again.
